      <bpmn2:documentation id="_TKId4DqfEfGeGeWP6G0fcQ"><![CDATA[Finds a free cage (or pluggable transceiver) on the selected edge equipment and returns the edge-equipment descriptor needed by the response.]]></bpmn2:documentation>
